据报道，雷德利·斯科特正在洽谈执导比吉斯传记片https://www.nme.com/news/music/ridley-scott-reportedly-in-talks-to-direct-bee-gees-biopic-3588338?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=ridley-scott-reportedly-in-与直接比吉斯传记片交谈Surej SinghFri, 16 Feb 2024 05:29:04 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3588338 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ridley-scott-bee-gees@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ridley-scott-bee-gees@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ridley-scott-bee-gees@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ridley-scott-bee-gees@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ridley-scott-bee-gees@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ridley-scott-bee-gees@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ridley-scott-bee-gees@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该片于2019年首播，历经多位导演</p><p>据报道<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ridley-scott-reportedly-in-talks-to-direct-bee-gees-biopic-3588338">，雷德利·斯科特正在洽谈导演比吉斯传记片的消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ridley-scott-bee-gees@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ridley-scott-bee-gees@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ridley-scott-bee-gees@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ridley-scott-bee-gees@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ridley-scott-bee-gees@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ridley-scott-bee-gees@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ridley-scott-bee-gees@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ridley-scott">，雷德利·斯科特</a>正在洽谈执导一部即将上映的基于<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bee-gees">比吉斯乐队的</a>传记片。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/music-biopics-best-to-see-before-you-die-3401944">生前值得一看的 50 部音乐传记片</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<a href="https://deadline.com/2024/02/ridley-scott-bee-gees-movie-1235827580/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>好莱坞截止日期</em></a>报道，接近该项目的匿名消息人士告诉该媒体，斯科特目前正与<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/paramount">派拉蒙影业公司</a>进行谈判，以执导即将上映的基于该团体的传记片。</p><p>这部电影目前尚未命名，尚未确定上映日期或演员阵容。据推测，斯科特还将与 GK Films 的格雷厄姆·金、Scott Free 的史黛西·斯奈德和迈克尔·普鲁斯共同制作这部电影。据报道，斯科特 2000 年史诗巨制《角斗士》的编剧约翰·洛根 (John Logan) 将执笔剧本。比吉斯最后一位幸存的兄弟和成员巴里·吉布 (Barry Gibb) 将担任执行制片人。</p><p>影片将讲述吉布斯兄弟巴里、莫里斯和罗宾的生活和事业故事，后两人分别于 2003 年和 2012 年去世。 </p><figure id="attachment_2849647" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2849647" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-2849647" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/beegees-2000x1270-1.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/beegees-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/beegees-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/beegees-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/beegees-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/beegees-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/beegees-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-2849647" class="wp-caption-text"> Bee Gees 于 20 世纪 70 年代演出。图片来源：MARKA / Alamy Stock Photo</figcaption></figure><p>派拉蒙影业多年来一直在制作比吉斯的传记片。它于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-bees-gees-biopic-way-producer-bohemian-rhapsody-2563401">2019 年首次宣布</a>，格雷厄姆·金 (Graham King) 同样热衷于农产品。两年后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_asia/news/film/kenneth-branagh-to-direct-new-bee-gees-biopic-2898827">宣布肯尼思·布拉纳将执导</a>这部电影，剧本由本·埃尔顿撰写。</p><p>布拉纳因不明原因退出该项目，约翰·卡尼于 2022 年 3 月接任总监，但因日程安排冲突而离开。 2022 年 12 月，《骗子》导演洛琳·斯卡法里亚 (Lorene Scafaria) 接替了他。</p><p> 《比吉斯》传记片是近期即将上映的一部以音乐家为背景的最新传记电影。根据<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/amy-winehouse">艾米·怀恩豪斯 (Amy Winehouse)</a>改编的《重返黑色》( <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/watch-the-first-official-teaser-for-amy-winehouse-biopic-back-to-black-3569022"><em>Back To Black)</em></a>已<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/watch-the-first-official-teaser-for-amy-winehouse-biopic-back-to-black-3569022">确定于 2024 年 4 月 12 日在英国上映</a>，并于 4 月 11 日在澳大利亚上映。这部电影以怀恩豪斯突破性的第二张也是最后一张录音室专辑命名，由<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/industry">《Industry》的</a></em>玛丽莎·阿贝拉 (Marisa Abela) 饰演怀恩豪斯本人，并概述了她在伦敦的生活以及她迅速成名的经历。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/watch-the-first-official-teaser-for-amy-winehouse-biopic-back-to-black-3569022">在这里观看电影的官方预告片</a>。</p><p>同样，一部基于<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-jackson">迈克尔·杰克逊的</a>传记片<em>《迈克尔》</em> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/first-look-at-michael-jacksons-nephew-jaafar-in-new-biopic-3586777"><em>目前正在制作中</em></a>。迈克尔·杰克逊现实生活中的侄子贾法尔饰演这位已故歌手，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/colman-domingo-cast-as-joe-jackson-in-michael-jackson-biopic-3577421">科蒙·多明戈则饰演他的父亲。</a></p><p>据报道<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ridley-scott-reportedly-in-talks-to-direct-bee-gees-biopic-3588338">，雷德利·斯科特正在洽谈导演比吉斯传记片的消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
